# Technical test scope

Source of truth: `Technical-Test.md`.

## Required features

- Login (seed user OK)
- Clients CRUD (name, company, email, phone, notes)
- Quotations CRUD + statuses: Draft, Sent, Approved, Rejected
- Quotation items with auto-calculated totals
- **AI draft** from client request text (backend-only AI call, validated JSON)
- **n8n webhook** when status → Approved

## Backend rules (when implementing)

- AI called from backend only - never expose API keys in frontend
- Validate AI JSON before save; `unit_price: null` when unknown
- Store prompt in `prompts/quotation-draft.md`
- Suggested API: see Technical-Test.md §5

## Submit artifacts

- README, demo login, n8n workflow JSON, AI prompt file, optional `/ai-notes.md`

## Current status

Web app is wired to FastAPI via `@repo/api` + TanStack Query. See `AUDIT.md` for gaps vs `Technical-Test.md` and enterprise issues.
